---
title: Pork Schnitzels & Oven-Baked Wedges with Apple-Parmesan Salad & Smokey Aioli
description: All the classic flavours in this German-inspired dish play off against each other in the most delightful way. The sweetness of the honey and apple against sharp Parmesan and crunchy crumbed pork is just lovely!
